comments: to memorize the words i tried to identify if there was a unique symbol or an unique disposition of certain symbols and give the items shown some kind of interpretation of what it could be and what it could be used for, that was relatively easy; this however hindered me in the actual test, because sometimes i would miss that particular pattern since i would not catch it in time before the word would disappear. I noticed some possible patterns about the symbols used and the items shown, I suspect these symbols are not like our language but like a combination of meanings, for example the items that had some particular geometrical shape and that could be used in some kind of construction or instrument had symbols that recalled geometry; while other items like the one resembling some kind of molecule had a symbol that was like a drop of water, maybe recalling biology or something organic; I noticed other patterns that I can't recall right now, perhaps if I could watch the items and the words again and taking my time I could explain myself in a more clear way.
